 and updates. Icons are sorted into categories in icon picker.</p><div class="hr">&nbsp;</div><a href="images/news/update124.jpg"><img class="image" style="float:left;margin:0 10px 10px 0;width:100px;height:100px;" src="resized/150-news/update124.jpg" alt="" /></a><div class="date">2013-06-17 12:00:00</div><h2>DCikonZ Theme v1.2.4 update</h2><p>Added 170 new icons + fixes and updates. And managed to reduce the size by half!</p><div class="hr">&nbsp;</div><a href="images/news/update123.jpg"><img class="image" style="float:left;margin:0 10px 10px 0;width:100px;height:100px;" src="resized/150-news/update123.jpg" alt="" /></a><div class="date">2013-06-08 12:00:00</div><h2>DCikonZ Theme v1.2.3 update</h2><p>Added 100 new icons + fixes and updates. New TSF Shell Wood theme :)</p><div class="hr">&nbsp;</div><a href="images/news/update122.jpg"><img class="image" style="float:left;margin:0 10px 10px 0;width:100px;height:100px;" src="resized/150-news/update122.jpg" alt="" /></a><div class="date">2013-05-23 12:00:00</div><h2>DCikonZ Theme v1.2.2 update</h2><p>Added 160 new icons + fixes and updates</p><div class="hr">&nbsp;</div><a href="images/news/update121.jpg"><img class="image" style="float:left;margin:0 10px 10px 0;width:100px;height:100px;" src="resized/150-news/update121.jpg" alt="" /></a><div class="date">2013-05-01 12:00:00</div><h2>DCikonZ Theme v1.2.1 update</h2><p>Added 140 new icons + fixes and updates</p><div class="hr">&nbsp;</div><a href="images/news/update120.jpg"><img class="image" style="float:left;margin:0 10px 10px 0;width:100px;height:100px;" src="resized/150-news/update120.jpg" alt="" /></a><div class="date">2013-03-29 12:00:00</div><h2>DCikonZ Theme v1.2.0 update</h2><p>Added 100 new icons + fixes and updates</p><div class="hr">&nbsp;</div><div class="date">2013-03-21 12:00:00</div><h2>DCikonZ Theme v1.1.9 update</h2><p>Added 150 new icons + fixes and updates + SmartLauncher support.</p><div class="hr">&nbsp;</div><div class="date">2013-03-03 12:00:00<