nZ Theme v1.0.6 update</h2><p>Added 50+ new icons.</p><div class="hr">&nbsp;</div><div class="date">2012-11-22 12:00:00</div><h2>DCikonZ Theme v1.0.5 update</h2><p>Fixed compatibility and added 35 new icons :)</p><div class="hr">&nbsp;</div><div class="date">2012-11-20 12:00:00</div><h2>DCikonZ Theme v1.0.5 beta2</h2><p>I think it's almost ready - theming and stuff. Fixed some bugs etc. Need testing and comments if You find something wrong :).</p><div class="hr">&nbsp;</div><div class="date">2012-11-18 12:00:00</div><h2>DCikonZ Theme v1.0.4 update</h2><p>Added 30 new icons :)</p><div class="hr">&nbsp;</div><div class="date">2012-11-18 12:00:00</div><h2>DCikonZ Theme v1.0.5 beta</h2><p>Fixed compatibility with all launchers, colors, docks etc. Need testing, can anyone help?</p><div class="hr">&nbsp;</div><div class="date">2012-11-15 12:00:00</div><h2>DCikonZ Theme v1.0.3 Google play update</h2><p>Added alternate icons for Phone, clock, messaging and browser :)<br />Now you can install this directly from Google play store (for free of course)</p><div class="hr">&nbsp;</div><div class="date">2012-11-12 12:00:00</div><h2>DCikonZ Theme v1.0.3 update</h2><p>Added almost 40 new icons :)</p><div class="hr">&nbsp;</div><div class="date">2012-11-11 12:00:00</div><h2>DCikonZ Theme v1.0.2 update</h2><p>Added 30 new icons :)</p><div class="hr">&nbsp;</div><div class="date">2012-11-05 12:00:00</div><h2>DCikonZ Theme v1.0.1 update</h2><p>Small update: this should be more compatible with AWD Launcher - selecting icons etc., and added 7 icons.</p><div class="hr">&nbsp;</div><div class="date">2012-11-04 12:00:00</div><h2>DCikonZ Theme v1.0.0 alpha</h2><p>I'm proud to present to you a set of icons that I made.<br />It should work with Nova, Apex, AWD and Go Launcher Ex ... I hope :)<br />This is a preliminary version, contains over 300 icons and 4 wallpapers, more icons will be added during the progress of work.</p><div class="hr">&nbsp;</div><div class="date">2012-11-03 12:00:00</div